syntax on
imap jk <Esc>
ino <down> <Nop>
ino <up> <Nop>
ino <left> <Nop>
ino <right> <Nop>
filetype plugin indent on
set number
nmap<C-down> <C-w>j
nmap<C-up> <C-w>k
nmap<C-left> <C-w>h
nmap<C-right> <C-w>l
 nmap<S-right> <C-w>>
  nmap<S-left> <C-w><
  nmap<S-down> <C-w>-
  nmap<S-up> <C-w>+
 
  " starcraft 2 position style:
  nmap m1 ma
  nmap m2 ms
  nmap m3 md
  nmap m4 mf
  nmap m5 mg
  nmap m6 mh
  nmap m7 mj
 nmap 11 'azz
  nmap 22 'szz
  nmap 33 'dzz
  nmap 44 'fzz
  nmap 55 'gzz
 nmap 66 'hzz
  nmap 77 'jzz
